Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.40,0:00:44.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石,如果你能来看一眼的话...\N{\rENG}Peridot, if you could come take a look at this...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.81,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在提醒我一下为什么我得听你的?\N{\rENG}Remind me again why I should listen to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,对\N{\rENG}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.95,0:00:51.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里的那个珍珠表现出了\N{\rENG}The Pearl here has exhibited
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}工程学方面的潜质-即使我很不愿承认,\N{\rENG}an aptitude for engineering that I begrudgingly respect,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.57,0:00:56.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但这解释不了她没完没了的歌唱,\N{\rENG}though that doesn't explain the spontaneous singing,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.11,0:00:58.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}尖叫,边唱边叫\N{\rENG}crying, singing while crying.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你干嘛给她那个?\N{\rENG}Why did you give her that?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}既然我们会坏了她所有的物品\N{\rENG}Well, we did destroy all her stuff.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.53,0:01:05.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得这或许能让她好过点\N{\rENG}I thought it might make her feel a little better.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.69,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}草包!浑身是泥的草包!\N{\rENG}Clods! Muddy clods!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}想不出别的方法来修饰"草包"了\N{\rENG}Running out of ways to say clods.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.02,0:01:13.43,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,我赶走那些奶牛了\N{\rENG}All right. I chased away those cows.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.57,0:01:15.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我们开工吧\N{\rENG}Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.11,0:01:19.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在我们开始前,你介意解除融合吗?\N{\rENG}Before we begin, would you mind unfusing?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.33,0:01:21.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这让我非常不爽\N{\rENG}It's making me incredibly uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.24,0:01:27.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤?我说了什么?\N{\rENG}What?! What'd I say?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们真得这么做吗?\N{\rENG}Do we really have to do that?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.37,0:01:32.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在这里的主导地位\N{\rENG}Her having free reign of the place
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.88,0:01:35.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我非常不爽\N{\rENG}made me incredibly uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给你,珍珠\N{\rENG}Here you go, Pearl.
Dialogue: 600,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.15,Hint,,0,0,0,,珍珠正在拆解的可能为波音747上使用的罗-罗RB211发动机（这怎么看出来的）
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,很好,嗯\N{\rENG}Oh, good. Hmm.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,不不不不\N{\rENG}No. No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我说我需要的是钨-钨啊\N{\rENG}I said I needed tungsten -- tungsten.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,钨是什么样子的?\N{\rENG}Uh, what does tungsten look like?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}钨(tungsten->tongue),恶!\N{\rENG}Tungsten. Ah!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.02,0:02:00.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}算了,我自己找吧\N{\rENG}Never mind. I'll just do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就缺某种杠杆优化器\N{\rENG}I just need some sort of leverage optimizer.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.57,0:02:09.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杠杆优化器?\N{\rENG}Leverage optimizer?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我说的就是那个\N{\rENG}That's what I said.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦!哈\N{\rENG}Oh! Ha.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是指你需要螺丝刀吗?\N{\rENG}You mean you want a screwdriver?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.77,0:02:15.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你有没有?\N{\rENG}Do you have one or not?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,为-为什么你不用这个?\N{\rENG}Uh, w-why don't you just use this one?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为那在我的可达半径之外\N{\rENG}Because it was outside my radius.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.06,0:02:21.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿,橄榄石,你管这个叫什么?\N{\rENG}Hey, Peridot, what do you call this?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.64,0:02:25.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}气味海绵体\N{\rENG}A scent sponge.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃?\N{\rENG}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,那这个呢?\N{\rENG}Okay, what's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.55,0:02:30.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}视觉球体\N{\rENG}Vision sphere.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石,那是-\N{\rENG}Peridot, that's --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等,史蒂文\N{\rENG}wait, wait, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石,这些呢?\N{\rENG}Peridot, these?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}触觉肢端\N{\rENG}Touch stumps.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个?\N{\rENG}This?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}重力连接器\N{\rENG}Gravity connectors.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.02,0:02:39.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个?\N{\rENG}This?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是你屁股!\N{\rENG}That's your butt!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.84,0:02:45.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,天啦,橄榄石,你要笑死我了!\N{\rENG}Oh, man, Peridot, you're killing me!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我才不会呢!那会破坏我们的休战协议\N{\rENG}I am not! That would violate our truce agreement.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.20,0:02:51.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不不不,你很幽默而已\N{\rENG}No, no, no. You're funny.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.64,0:02:53.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}幽默?\N{\rENG}Funny?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.60,0:02:54.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石,如果你能将\N{\rENG}Peridot, if you can get
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.93,0:02:56.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}磁铁从微波炉中取出来,\N{\rENG}the magnetron out of that microwave,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.87,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们就有了所有需要的东西\N{\rENG}we'll have everything we need --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}除了钻头以外\N{\rENG}except for the drill head.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么不用幼儿园的\N{\rENG}Why don't I just get an injector drill head
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}注射器的钻头呢?\N{\rENG}from the kindergarten?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.82,0:03:04.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.44,0:03:07.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其实,我想你可以试试那个\N{\rENG}Well, I guess that's something you could try.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她不能独自去幼儿园\N{\rENG}She's not going to the kindergarten
